name: ValueSetR5EndpointPayloadTypeForR4
title: Cross-version ValueSet R5.EndpointPayloadType for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version ValueSet represents content from http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/endpoint-payload-type|5.0.0 for use in FHIR R4 that is appropriate for use but unavailable in `http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/endpoint-payload-type|4.0.1`.
purpose:
This value set is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
value set `http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/endpoint-payload-type|5.0.0` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source value set is bound to the following FHIR R5 elements:
* `Endpoint.payload.type` as Example

Across FHIR versions, the value set has been mapped as:
* `http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/endpoint-payload-type|5.0.0`
* `http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/endpoint-payload-type|4.3.0`
* `http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/endpoint-payload-type|4.0.1`
